@startuml
' Backend-only view for Add Visit flow

title Add Visit Flow - Backend Only

autonumber

actor "API Client\n<<External Caller>>" as Client
participant "OwnerRestController\n<<Backend REST Controller>>" as OwnerCtrl
participant "VisitMapper\n<<Backend Mapper>>" as VisitMapper
participant "VisitRepository\n<<Backend Repository>>" as VisitRepo
database "Database\n<<Relational DB>>" as DB

Client -> OwnerCtrl : POST /api/owners/{ownerId}/pets/{petId}/visits\nbody: VisitFieldsDto
OwnerCtrl -> VisitMapper : toVisit(visitFieldsDto)
VisitMapper --> OwnerCtrl : Visit (without pet)
OwnerCtrl -> VisitRepo : save(visit)
VisitRepo -> DB : INSERT visits(pet_id, visit_date, description)
DB --> VisitRepo : generated visit id
VisitRepo --> OwnerCtrl : persisted Visit
OwnerCtrl --> Client : 201 Created

alt Invalid payload / validation error
  OwnerCtrl --> Client : 400 Bad Request (ProblemDetail)
else Missing related resource (contract)
  OwnerCtrl --> Client : 404 Not Found
else Unexpected persistence/runtime error
  OwnerCtrl --> Client : 500 Internal Server Error (ProblemDetail)
end

@enduml

